{"type": "article", "id": 25310, "title": "弹性挂钩", "description": "", "date": "2016-04-12T06:35:03Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 29, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607122944fz8rWqsv7KFjYOQh.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">你常常在洗澡时将洗发水和沐浴露放在地上吗？不断的弯腰拿取多少有些不方便吧。来自丹麦的设计师 Flávia Arantes Jensen 就设计了一个挂洗护用品的挂钩，是用硅胶做的，挂钩连接了两圈有弹性的环来固定洗护用品，最大可承担 1.5kg。产品已完成了众筹，<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/568728991/bungee-bath-sleek-fun-in-the-shower/description\">这里是众筹链接</a>。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607122941LhMP5IQNYelusc49.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.4\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071229422s5pMWmfwGbzLcK0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.295\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607122942HKMIjJkq528CSYRN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.34537037\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"placeholder\"></figure><figure class=\"placeholder\"></figure><figure class=\"placeholder\"></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607122943hmFxvaLock8DEV4O.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.415\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071229434x38oI1WA0vc2PHg.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.06333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n\n\n"}